data.description: Step into the inviting embrace of this charming ranch-style haven that seamlessly combines comfort and style. The 1856 sq ft of finished space welcomes you with new carpet throughout the main floor, creating a warm and cozy ambiance. Explore three bedrooms on the main level, each thoughtfully designed for restful nights. Venture downstairs to discover a versatile non-conforming bedroom, perfect for guests or a home office and a large finished rec room. The two bathrooms provide convenience, while the fully fenced backyard beckons with a delightful patio – an outdoor sanctuary for gatherings and relaxation. This home is not just a space; it's a lifestyle, offering the ease of an assumable VA loan. Don't miss the chance to make this residence yours – schedule a tour today and envision the possibilities that await at 4910 N 17th St.
